(REFUND AND RETURN POLICY) Tj
T*
(Last updated: January 2025) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(OVERVIEW) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If something is not right,) Tj
T*
(we will work to make it right. This policy explains how to initiate a return, which) Tj
T*
(items are eligible, how refunds are processed, and what to expect at every step.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(1. RETURN ELIGIBILITY) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.1 Standard Return Window) Tj
T*
(Most items can be returned within 30 days of the delivery date. Items must be:) Tj
T*
(- In their original, unused condition) Tj
T*
(- In the original packaging with all tags, accessories, and documentation included) Tj
T*
(- Free from damage caused by the customer) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.2 Extended Return Window) Tj
T*
(We offer an extended 60-day return window for:) Tj
T*
(- Items purchased during major sale events \(Black Friday, Cyber Monday, holiday) Tj
T*
(promotions\)) Tj
T*
(- Orders placed by verified members of our loyalty program at Gold tier or above) Tj
T*
(- Items marked "Extended Returns Eligible" on the product page) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.3 Non-Returnable Items) Tj
T*
(The following cannot be returned:) Tj
T*
(- Digital downloads and software license keys once activated or downloaded) Tj
T*
(- Gift cards and store credit) Tj
T*
(- Perishable goods \(food, flowers, live plants\)) Tj
T*
(- Hazardous materials and flammable liquids) Tj
T*
(- Custom or personalized items \(engraved, monogrammed, made-to-order\)) Tj
T*
(- Intimate apparel, swimwear, and pierced jewelry for hygiene reasons \(unless) Tj
T*
(defective\)) Tj
T*
(- Items marked "Final Sale" at the time of purchase) Tj
T*
(- Opened consumable products \(cosmetics, supplements, batteries\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.4 Partial Returns) Tj
T*
(You may return individual items from a multi-item order. Refunds are calculated per) Tj
T*
(item based on the price paid, minus any applicable restocking fees or proportional) Tj
T*
(discounts applied to the order.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(2. HOW TO INITIATE A RETURN) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
