(2.1 Online Return Portal) Tj
T*
(The fastest way to start a return is through our self-service portal:) Tj
T*
(1. Log into your account and go to Order History) Tj
T*
(2. Select the order and click "Return or Exchange") Tj
T*
(3. Choose the item\(s\) you wish to return and select a reason) Tj
T*
(4. Select whether you prefer a refund or an exchange) Tj
T*
(5. Print the prepaid return shipping label \(if eligible\) or choose to ship at your) Tj
T*
(own cost) Tj
T*
(6. Pack the item securely and drop it off at the indicated carrier location) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.2 Guest Orders) Tj
T*
(If you checked out as a guest, initiate your return by emailing) Tj
T*
(support@shopexample.com with your order number, the item\(s\) to return, and your) Tj
T*
(reason. We will send you instructions within 1 business day.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.3 In-Store Returns) Tj
T*
(If you purchased online, you may return eligible items at any of our physical store) Tj
T*
(locations. Bring the item with its original packaging and your order confirmation) Tj
T*
(email or receipt. In-store returns are refunded to the original payment method within) Tj
T*
(5 business days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(3. RETURN SHIPPING) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.1 Free Returns \(Defective or Our Error\)) Tj
T*
(If you received a defective item, a wrong item, or your order was damaged in transit,) Tj
T*
(we will provide a prepaid return label at no cost to you.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.2 Customer-Initiated Returns) Tj
T*
(For change-of-mind returns, we offer a prepaid label for a $6.99 deduction from your) Tj
T*
(refund, or you may ship at your own expense using any carrier. If you ship at your) Tj
T*
(own expense, use a service with tracking and retain your receipt ? we are not) Tj
T*
(responsible for packages lost during return transit.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.3 International Returns) Tj
T*
(Customers outside the United States are responsible for all return shipping costs and) Tj
T*
(any duties or taxes associated with the return. We do not provide prepaid) Tj
T*
(international return labels.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.4 Return Shipment Requirements) Tj
T*
(- Use a sturdy box; do not use the product box alone as the outer shipping box) Tj
T*
(- Include a copy of your packing slip or a note with your order number inside) Tj
T*
(- Do not write on or attach labels directly to the product's retail packaging) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(4. REFUND PROCESSING) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
