(4.1 Inspection Period) Tj
T*
(Once we receive your return, our team inspects it within 2 to 3 business days. You) Tj
T*
(will receive an email confirming receipt and the inspection outcome.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.2 Approved Refunds) Tj
T*
(Approved refunds are issued within 3 to 5 business days of inspection approval. The) Tj
T*
(refund is returned to the original payment method used at checkout. This means:) Tj
T*
(- Credit or debit card: 3 to 10 business days to appear depending on your bank) Tj
T*
(- PayPal: 3 to 5 business days) Tj
T*
(- Store credit: applied immediately to your account) Tj
T*
(- Buy Now Pay Later \(BNPL\) plans: handled in accordance with the BNPL provider's) Tj
T*
(refund policy) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.3 Partial Refunds) Tj
T*
(We may issue a partial refund \(typically 15 to 25% less than the original price\) for) Tj
T*
(items that:) Tj
T*
(- Are returned without original packaging) Tj
T*
(- Show signs of use that reduce resale value) Tj
T*
(- Are missing accessories or documentation that was included at original sale) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.4 Denied Refunds) Tj
T*
(Refunds may be denied if:) Tj
T*
(- The item is clearly used beyond reasonable inspection) Tj
T*
(- The item does not match what was purchased \(wrong item sent back\)) Tj
T*
(- The return window has expired) Tj
T*
(- The item falls under a non-returnable category) Tj
T*
(You will be notified by email if your return is denied. Denied items can be shipped) Tj
T*
(back to you at your expense.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.5 Restocking Fees) Tj
T*
(A restocking fee of 15% applies to:) Tj
T*
(- Electronics returned after 15 days from delivery) Tj
T*
(- Large furniture and appliances) Tj
T*
(- Special-order items not normally stocked) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(5. EXCHANGES) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.1 How to Exchange) Tj
T*
(Select "Exchange" when initiating your return in the portal. Choose the replacement) Tj
T*
(item \(same product in a different size/color, or a different product\). If the) Tj
T*
(replacement costs more, you will be charged the difference. If it costs less, the) Tj
T*
(difference is refunded to your original payment method.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.2 Exchange Shipping) Tj
T*
(Standard exchanges ship free via standard shipping once we receive and inspect your) Tj
T*
(returned item. If you need the replacement faster, select expedited shipping at) Tj
T*
(checkout \(additional fee applies\).) Tj
ET
