(6. DEFECTIVE AND DAMAGED ITEMS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.1 Item Arrived Defective) Tj
T*
(If your item was defective on arrival, contact us within 30 days of delivery. We will) Tj
T*
(offer:) Tj
T*
(- A full replacement shipped at no cost) Tj
T*
(- A full refund with a prepaid return label) Tj
T*
(- A repair or service credit, where applicable) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.2 Damage in Transit) Tj
T*
(Report transit damage within 7 days of delivery. Include photos of the outer) Tj
T*
(packaging and the damaged item. We will file a carrier claim and issue a replacement) Tj
T*
(or refund once the claim is processed \(typically 5 to 10 business days\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.3 Manufacturer Defects After Use) Tj
T*
(Defects that appear during normal use after delivery may be covered by the) Tj
T*
(manufacturer's warranty rather than our return policy. See the Product Warranty) Tj
T*
(Policy or the documentation included with your item for warranty details. We can) Tj
T*
(assist in connecting you with the manufacturer.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(7. ORDER CANCELLATIONS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.1 Before Shipment) Tj
T*
(Orders can be cancelled at no charge if they have not yet entered the processing or) Tj
T*
(fulfillment stage. Go to Order History and click "Cancel Order" to request) Tj
T*
(cancellation. If eligible, the full amount is refunded to the original payment method) Tj
T*
(within 3 to 5 business days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.2 After Shipment) Tj
T*
(Once an order has shipped, it cannot be cancelled. You will need to wait for delivery) Tj
T*
(and then initiate a return following the standard process.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.3 Pre-order Cancellations) Tj
T*
(Pre-orders can be cancelled at any time before the estimated ship date for a full) Tj
T*
(refund.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(8. GIFT RETURNS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
